00:43:51.579 --> 00:43:55.930
limit when he climbed on board that ship.

00:43:55.930 --> 00:43:56.930
But he fought it.

00:43:56.930 --> 00:43:58.140
His lawyers fought it hard.

00:43:58.140 --> 00:44:01.819
There was some ambiguity in the evidence and
he was not convicted.

00:44:01.819 --> 00:44:06.930
So, let's say there was doubt about whether
Hazelwood was drunk when he was captaining

00:44:06.930 --> 00:44:09.339
a supertanker.

00:44:09.339 --> 00:44:13.170
What there was no doubt about was that he
