00:44:13.170 --> 00:44:15.130
His mother testified.

00:44:15.130 --> 00:44:17.589
She had known he had a problem with alcohol.

00:44:17.589 --> 00:44:22.920
In 1985, four years before the accident, Exxon
had treated him for his problem with alcohol.

00:44:22.920 --> 00:44:26.380
After the accident, Exxon's President said
he "thought he had mastered the problem."

00:44:26.380 --> 00:44:31.119
But in 1986, he had his driver's license revoked
for a DUI.

00:44:31.119 --> 00:44:34.849
In 1988, he had his driver's license revoked
for a DUI.

00:44:34.849 --> 00:44:39.559
At the time he was captaining a supertanker,
